description:
This is a 6 minute workout called 'Instructional: Hip Pivot' from the channel Aisyah Rafaee.
The workout falls under Warm-up/Warm-up.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Masterclass Workout and The Comfort Moves vibe.
The The Masterclass Workout vibe means Technique-driven, focused, skill-building. This is especially good for Those who love precision and mastery in movement. The The Comfort Moves vibe means Safe, cozy, feel-good movement. This is especially good for Those who want to move but need it to feel easy and accessible..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Learn how to build power through your hip pivot with Aisyah during this drill from the Four Seasons in L.A. ...
